title: UGG Australia: How to Style the Jena boot
description:
Statement-making style mavens will love this New Orleans-inspired military boot, designed with a removable kiltie and rich brogue detailing. Convertible in nature, this lace-up boot can be worn cuffed up or down, transitioning seamlessly from polished to playful.

#UGGStyle Fall 2013
